---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import { SITE_DESCRIPTION, SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<h1>The Setup Vault: Home Office Setup Guides & Desk Accessories</h1>
			<p>
				The Setup Vault is a home office resource built around one goal: helping you pick the
				right desk accessories the first time, without wading through generic, padded-out
				reviews. We cover the practical gear that makes a home office actually work — laptop
				stands, desk lamps, monitor stands, cable organizers, desk pads, USB hubs, webcams,
				wireless keyboard and mouse combos, wireless charging pads, and desk fans.
			</p>
			<p>
				Every guide is built around a specific buying question — not "here's a product," but
				"here's what to look for, what the tradeoffs are, and who this actually isn't for."
				Whether you're setting up a permanent home office desk setup or upgrading one piece at
				a time, our goal is to save you the research time.
			</p>
			<p>
				<a href="/blog">Browse all our home office and desk setup guides →</a>
			</p>
			<p>
				Learn more about how we choose what to recommend on our
				<a href="/about">About & Affiliate Disclosure page</a>.
			</p>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
